0to%20adjust%20to%20using%20the%20MW75%20Neuro%20while%20working.%20It%20was%20occasionally%20a%20chore%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20headphones%2C%20open%20the%20app%20to%20start%20a%20Focus%20Session%2C%20and%20then%20use%20the%20headphones%20for%20extended%20periods%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20much%20like%20running%20with%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-apple-watch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Watch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20the%20headphones%20and%20app%20became%20a%20routine%20as%20I%20grew%20to%20hate%20missing%20out%20on%20capturing%20my%20focus%20data.%20Knowing%20I%20could%20record%20and%20analyze%20my%20brain%20activity%20helped%20encourage%20me%20to%20use%20them%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20start%20a%20Focus%20Session%2C%20the%20app%20prompts%20you%20to%20select%20the%20type%20of%20activity%20you'll%20be%20engaging%20in%20(work%2C%20entertainment%2C%20study%2C%20etc.).%20You%20can%20also%20leave%20notes%20about%20what%20you'd%20like%20to%20accomplish%20during%20the%20session.%20Once%20you%20end%20the%20session%2C%20you're%20prompted%20to%20score%20how%20productive%20you%20felt.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20will%20then%20sync%20your%20data%20to%20provide%20a%20full%20report%20that%20shows%20your%20focus%20levels%20on%20a%20chart%20over%20the%20duration%20of%20your%20session.%20You%20even%20get%20points%20based%20on%20how%20many%20minutes%20of%20high%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20low%20focus%20you%20achieved%2C%20and%20the%20app%20tries%20to%20further%20gamify%20concentration%20by%20encouraging%20you%20to%20achieve%20100%20points%20every%20day.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246ad27da-9c9a-4fdc-8886-0a3e1ceba555%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Focus-tracking%5C%22%3EMy%20results%20showed%20a%20mix%20of%20low-focus%20lulls%20and%20high-concentration%20peaks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20from%20the%20Neurable%20app%20showing%20Focus%20Session%20results.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f6e7eb4be2fff9a219c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221871%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20app%20shows%20your%20results%20with%20data%20for%20high%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20low%20focus%20periods.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FNeurable%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20several%20Focus%20Sessions%20with%20the%20Neurable%20app%20to%20move%20past%20the%20novelty.%20At%20first%2C%20my%20mind%20would%20wander%20to%20the%20headphones%2C%20leaving%20me%20wondering%20how%20they%20were%20processing%20my%20activity%20when%20an%20email%20came%20in%20or%20when%20I%20reached%20for%20my%20phone.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20moved%20past%20this%20and%20used%20the%20MW75%20Neuro%20without%20thinking%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20app%20results%20were%20often%20scattered%2C%20but%20they%20also%20felt%20obvious.%20Can%20you%20be%20a%20writer%20and%20not%20work%20in%20short%20bursts%20of%20inspired%20creativity%20and%20instant%20distractions%3F%20My%20sessions%20showed%20lots%20of%20low-focus%20periods%20with%20a%20few%20high%20spikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20the%20headphones%20primarily%20at%20my%20desk%2C%20but%20I%20also%20tested%20them%20while%20watching%20movies%20and%20during%20other%20activities.%20The%20most%20interesting%20result%20I%20experienced%20was%20during%20a%20phone%20call%20that%20showed%20high%20focus%20for%20the%20entire%2015-minute%20call.%20The%20data%20matched%20how%20concentrated%20I%20felt%20during%20the%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d74d4d2-b95a-4517-b1ba-76f2ff915952%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%5C%22%3EThe%20focus-tracking%20tech%20is%20cool%2C%20but%20its%20usefulness%20is%20limited%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20Neurable%20logo%20on%20the%20headband%20of%20the%20MW75%20Neuro%20headphones.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679406bc196626c4098500a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20MW75%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%2C%20but%20there's%20room%20for%20improvement.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20neat%20as%20the%20focus-tracking%20technology%20is%2C%20its%20practical%20utility%20feels%20lacking%20in%20certain%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20for%20my%20working%20habits.%20Based%20on%20my%20existing%20preference%20for%20writing%20in%20short%20bursts%2C%20I%20rarely%20triggered%20the%20app%20to%20send%20notifications%20prompting%20me%20to%20take%20a%20break.%20And%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20lost%20focus%20%3Cem%3Ebefore%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%20was%20alerted%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I'm%20easily%20distracted%20by%20an%20incoming%20email%20or%20message%20that%20will%20derail%20my%20writing%20for%20five%20to%2010%20minutes%2C%20I%20use%20that%20%26quot%3Bdistracted%26quot%3B%20time%20to%20consider%20my%20thoughts.%20Then%2C%20I'm%20back%20to%20writing%20more.%20Whether%20intentional%20or%20not%2C%20these%20headphones%20feel%20like%20a%20sophisticated%20tool%20for%20people%20who%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FPomodoro_Technique%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPomodoro%20Technique%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%20of%20relying%20on%20a%20timer%20for%20breaks%2C%20they%20could%20tap%20into%20a%20more%20natural%20rhythm%20dictated%20by%20their%20own%20concentration%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scope%20of%20the%20MW75%20Neuro%20headphones%20is%20narrow%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20expanded%20with%20only%20a%20few%20tweaks.%20I%20would%20love%20to%20see%20a%20setting%20in%20the%20app%20to%20allow%20me%20to%20bump%20up%20or%20down%20the%20aggressiveness%20of%20its%20focus%20alerts.%20It%20would%20also%20be%20cool%20to%2