r.%3Cp%3EMelina%20Mara%2FPool%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Trump%20on%20Tuesday%20rolled%20back%20a%2060-year-old%20antidiscrimination%20executive%20order.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%2C%20one%20of%20several%20anti-DEI%20changes%20he's%20made%20so%20far%2C%20has%20consequences%20for%20the%20private%20sector.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20what%20Trump's%20Equal%20Employment%20Opportunity%20decision%20means%20and%20how%20it%20affects%20businesses%20and%20workers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-davos-speech-world-economic-forum-eu-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20revoked%20a%20civil%20rights-era%20Equal%20Employment%20Opportunity%20executive%20order%2C%20one%20of%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-day-one-agenda-executive-orders-inauguration-day-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweeping%20changes%20he's%20made%20since%20taking%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hamper%20DEI%20and%20reshape%20the%20federal%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20guts%20federal%20contract%20workers'%20protections%20from%20discrimination%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20characteristics%20like%20race%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20his%20decision%20means%20for%20businesses%20and%20workers%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e7d2e9f-f0f3-4e22-ac00-4204c3ad6753%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20Equal%20Employment%20Opportunity%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EExecutive%20Order%2011246%2C%20issued%20by%20President%20Lyndon%20B.%20Johnson%20in%201965%2C%20prohibited%20federal%20contractors%20from%20discriminating%20in%20employment%20and%20required%20them%20to%20take%20affirmative%20action%20to%20ensure%20equal%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2060-year-old%20act%20has%20been%20amended%20and%20strengthened%20over%20the%20years%20to%20protect%20federal%20contract%20workers%20from%20discrimination%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20characteristics%20like%20race%2C%20color%2C%20religion%2C%20sex%2C%20sexual%20orientation%2C%20gender%20identity%2C%20and%20national%20origin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Labor's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dol.gov%2Fagencies%2Fofccp%2Fabout%2Fexecutive-order-11246-history%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20calls%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20key%20landmark%20in%20a%20series%20of%20federal%20actions%20aimed%20at%20ending%20racial%2C%20religious%20and%20ethnic%20discrimination%26quot%3B%20and%20notes%20that%20workers%20employed%20by%20federal%20contractors%20represent%20roughly%2020%25%20of%20the%20US%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2280a0faae-5dd0-4c07-a8c1-d44f7ae5d7f8%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20change%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20decision%20requires%20the%20Labor%20Department's%20Office%20of%20Federal%20Contract%20Compliance%20Programs%20to%20stop%20promoting%20diversity%20and%20to%20stop%20holding%20federal%20contractors%20and%20subcontractors%20responsible%20for%20taking%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20directs%20the%20office%20to%20stop%20%26quot%3Ballowing%20or%20encouraging%20Federal%20contractors%20and%20subcontractors%20to%20engage%20in%20workforce%20balancing%20based%20on%20race%2C%20color%2C%20sex%2C%20sexual%20preference%2C%20religion%2C%20or%20national%20origin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20of%20federal%20contractors%20and%20subcontractors%20still%20have%20some%20protections%20under%20the%20Civil%20Rights%20Act%20of%201964%2C%20and%20may%20have%20additional%20protections%20under%20state%20or%20local%20laws%2C%20Stefanie%20Camfield%2C%20associate%20general%20counsel%20of%20Engage%20PEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a792b9b-ce4b-4de7-bb7b-df16f167ce70%5C%22%3EWhy%20did%20Trump%20make%20this%20decision%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConservatives%20have%20increasingly%20taken%20aim%20at%20%3Cspan%3Eefforts%20related%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eto%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoke-capitalism-reversal-google-unilever-bud-light-esg-dei-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20DEI%20and%20social%20and%20environmental%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Trump%20has%20made%20no%20secret%20of%20his%20disdain%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-day-one-agenda-executive-orders-inauguration-day-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esigned%20an%20executive%20order%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20terminate%20DEI%20mandates%2C%20policies%2C%20programs%2C%20preferences%2C%20and%20activities%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bradical%20and%20wasteful%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20federal%20government.%20Federal%20agencies%20were%20told%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-orders-federal-dei-roles-terminated-staff-on-leave-immediately-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20employees%20in%20DEI%20roles%20on%20paid%20leave%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20meantime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd467e71-71f8-4904-8497-b38ac081da6c%5C%22%3EHow%20are%20people%20responding%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20anti-DEI%20conservatives%20are%20celebrating%20Trump's%20decision%2C%20labor%20advocates%20and%20leaders%20of%20marginalized%20people's%20groups%20have%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20executive%20order%20reversal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudy%20Conti%2C%20government%20affairs%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Employment%20Law%20Project%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nelp.org%2Ftrump-abandons-workplace-discrimination-protections-federal-contractors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Trump%20had%20%26quot%3Bgutted%20key%20tools%20to%20prevent%20discrimination%20and%20