a%20reporter%20from%20Russian%20state%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20Trump%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmart%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpragmatic%26quot%3B%20man%2C%20Putin%20also%20repeated%20the%20Republican's%20unfounded%20claim%20that%20he%20won%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20against%20Joe%20Biden%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20but%20agree%20with%20him%20that%20if%20he%20had%20been%20president%20--%20if%20his%20victory%20hadn't%20been%20stolen%20in%202020%20--%20then%20maybe%20there%20would%20not%20have%20been%20the%20crisis%20in%20Ukraine%20that%20emerged%20in%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPressure%20from%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nearly%20three-year%20Ukraine%20conflict%20has%20plunged%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20nuclear%20powers%20to%20their%20lowest%20levels%20since%20the%20Cold%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20who%20was%20inaugurated%20on%20Monday%2C%20has%20called%20the%20conflict%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%26quot%3B%20and%20threatened%20Russia%20with%20tougher%20economic%20sanctions%20if%20it%20does%20not%20agree%20to%20stop%20its%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20don't%20settle%20this%20war%20soon%2C%20like%20almost%20immediately%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20put%20massive%20tariffs%20on%20Russia%2C%20and%20massive%20taxes%2C%20and%20also%20big%20sanctions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Republican%20said%20during%20a%20Fox%20News%20interview%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20would%20ask%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20OPEC%20to%20lower%20oil%20prices%2C%20claiming%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20price%20came%20down%2C%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20would%20end%20immediately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20pushed%20back%20at%20Trump's%20claim%20that%20lower%20oil%20prices%20might%20expedite%20the%20end%20of%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E