%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117529407%2Cimgsize-68340.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fangry-h-1b-tweet-or-hindu-faith-why-was-vivek-ramaswamy-really-fired-from-doge%2Farticleshow%2F117526472.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117526472.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fangry-h-1b-tweet-or-hindu-faith-why-was-vivek-ramaswamy-really-fired-from-doge%2Farticleshow%2F117526472.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fangry-h-1b-tweet-or-hindu-faith-why-was-vivek-ramaswamy-really-fired-from-doge%2Famp_articleshow%2F117526472.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fangry-h-1b-tweet-or-hindu-faith-why-was-vivek-ramaswamy-really-fired-from-doge%2Famp_articleshow%2F117526472.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCentre%2C%20States%2C%20All%20Parties%20Are%20To%20Blame%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex%20RBI%20Chief%20On%20Freebies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFreebies%20are%20desirable%20but%20there%20has%20got%20to%20be%20restraint%20as%20they%20are%20an%20enormous%20fiscal%20burden%2C%20former%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20governor%20Subba%20Rao%20Duvvuri%20told%20NDTV%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20full%20Union%20Budget%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance's%20(NDA)%20third%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubba%20Rao%2C%20who%20served%20as%20RBI%20chief%20for%20five%20years%20from%202008%20to%202013%2C%20cautioned%20that%20freebies%20do%20not%20necessarily%20result%20in%20any%20political%20gain%2C%20and%20both%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20are%20to%20blame%20for%20the%20freebies%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20message%20they%20%5Bgovernment%5D%20can%20send%20with%20respect%20to%20fiscal%20responsibility%20is%20about%20freebies.%20We%20have%20seen%20freebies%3B%20we%20saw%20them%20during%20the%20Maharashtra%20elections.%20We%20have%20seen%20them%20today%20ahead%20of%20the%20Delhi%20elections.%20And%20I%20know%20it's%20difficult%20to%20apportion%20blame%2C%26quot%3B%20Subba%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20central%20government%2C%20state%20governments%2C%20and%20all%20political%20parties%20are%20to%20blame.%20I%20don't%20believe%20that%20it%20%5Bfreebies%5D%20is%20paying%20any%20political%20dividends%20because%20if%20every%20party%20is%20offering%20freebies%2C%20no%20party%20gets.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it's%20an%20enormous%20fiscal%20burden%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20RBI%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20a%20poor%20country%20like%20India%2C%20transfer%20payments%20are%20essential%20and%20even%20desirable%20in%20difficult%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20there%20has%20got%20to%20be%20restraint%20because%20these%20subsidies%20or%20freebies%20are%20being%20financed%20out%20of%20debt%2C%20and%20a%20debt%20has%20to%20repay%20itself.%20One%20message%20the%20central%20government%20can%20send%20to%20mean%20business%20is%20to%20say%20that%20we%20are%20going%20to%20initiate%20-%20what%20if%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20announces%20in%20the%20Budget%20-%20that%20I'm%20going%20to%20initiate%20a%20dialogue%20with%20all%20political%20parties%2C%20all%20governments%20adopting%20a%20code%20of%20conduct%20on%20freebies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Subba%20Rao%2C%20who%20went%20in%20as%20RBI%20chief%20just%20a%20week%20before%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis%20began%20in%20September%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20it%20%5Bdialogue%5D%20will%20be%20in%20the%20collective%20good%20of%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Economic%20Growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubba%20Rao%20said%20opinion%20is%20divided%20on%20why%20economic%20growth%20slowed%20down%20to%205.4%20per%20cent.%20One%20view%20is%20that%20it%20is%20cyclical%2C%20and%20government%20expenditure%20slowed%20because%20of%20elections%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20now%20with%20elections%20behind%2C%20government%20expenditure%20and%20growth%20will%20pick%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20against%20that%2C%20there%20is%20another%20view%20which%20is%20that%20the%20slowdown%20is%20structural%2C%20that%20the%20rapid%20growth%20we%20saw%20over%20the%20last%20three-four%20years%20is%20because%20of%20a%20rebound%20from%20the%20COVID%20dip%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Taxes%20Be%20Reduced%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubba%20Rao%20said%20cutting%20taxes%20is%20not%20appropriate%20for%20the%20situation%20India%20is%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20despite%20urban%20consumption%20slowing%20and%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%20(GST)%20collections%20rising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20short%20answer%20is%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20RBI%20chief%20said%20to%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20can%20reduce%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20here's%20a%20considerate%20reply.%20If%20you%20can%20afford%20it%2C%20that's%20a%20way%20of%20doing%20it.%20Because%20what%20you're%20asking%20or%20what%20you're%20saying%20is%20standard%20supply%20side%20economics.%20Cut%20taxes%2C%20that'll%20spur%20production%2C%20that'll%20spur%20consumption%2C%20and%20we'll%20get%20on%20to%20our%20growth%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20that%20is%20not%20appropriate%20for%20our%20situation%20now%20because%20it'll%20at%20best%20be%20a%20temporary%20palliative.%20It%20cannot%20improve%20consumption%20on%20a%20long%20term%20basis.%20What%20we%20need%20to%20do%20is%20give%20people%20long%20term%20income%2C%20not%20just%20short%20term%20palliatives.%20Besides%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20government%20can%20afford%20to%20cut%20taxes%2C%20given%20the%20fiscal%20constraints%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Subba%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20RBI%2C%20Subba%20Rao%20was%20a%20Distinguished%20Visiting%20Fellow%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%20(2014-18)%20and%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20(2019-20).%20Most%20recently%2C%20he%20was%20a%20Senior%20Fellow%20at%20Yale%20Jackson%20School%20of%20Global%20Affairs%20(2023).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737733980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F2ulmdmvg_subba-rao-duvvuri-_625x300_24_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-budget-2025-centre-states-all-parties-are-to-blame-says-ex-rbi-governor-subba-rao-on-freebies-7551366%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Freebies%20are%20desirable%20but%20there%20has%20got%20to%20be%20restraint%20as%20they%20are%20an%20enormous%20fiscal%20burden%2C%20former%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20governor%20Subba%20Rao%20Duvvuri%20told%20NDTV%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20full%20Union%20Budget%20of%20the%20NDA's%20third%20consecutive%20term.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-budget-2025-centre-states-all-parties-are-to-blame-says-ex-rbi-governor-subba-rao-on-freebies-7551366%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vivek%20Agnihotri%20calls%20Jasleen%20Royal%20%E2%80%98auto-tuned%20singer%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737733856000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117529335%2Cimgsize-30190.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvivek-agnihotri-criticizes-jasleen-royals-coldplay-opening-act-calls-her-an-auto