uary%2020th%20since%20the%20new%20administration%20has%20indicated%20stricter%20immigration%20rules%20and%20tighter%20enforcements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20students%20can%20work%20in%20the%20US%20on%20F-1%20visas%20for%20up%20to%2020%20hours%20a%20week%20on-campus%2C%20but%20many%20students%20work%20off-campus%20at%20restaurants%2C%20gas%20stations%2C%20retail%20stores%20and%20more%20to%20cover%20essential%20expenses.%20However%2C%20students%20are%20giving%20up%20such%20jobs%20now%20to%20safeguard%20their%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20work%20in%20a%20small%20caf%C3%A9%20after%20my%20college%20hours%20to%20cover%20my%20monthly%20expenses.%20I%20earned%20%247%20per%20hour%20and%20worked%20six%20hours%20every%20day.%20%26quot%3BThough%20it%20was%20a%20comfortable%20arrangement%2C%20I%20quit%20last%20week%20after%20hearing%20that%20immigration%20authorities%20might%20crack%20down%20on%20unauthorised%20work.%20I%20can't%20take%20any%20chances%2C%20especially%20after%20borrowing%20%2450%2C000%20(Rs%2042.5%20lakh%20approx.)%20to%20study%20here%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Arjun%2C%20a%20graduate%20student%20in%20Illinois.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Neha%2C%20a%20Master's%20student%20in%20New%20York%2C%20had%20her%20concerns.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe've%20heard%20talk%20about%20random%20checks%20at%20workplaces.%20So%2C%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20stop%20working%20for%20now.%20It's%20hard%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20risk%20deportation%20or%20losing%20our%20student%20visa%20status.%20My%20parents%20have%20already%20sacrificed%20too%20much%20to%20send%20me%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20said%20that%20they%20will%20assess%20the%20current%20situation%20before%20deciding%20whether%20to%20restart%20their%20part-time%20jobs.%20Till%20that%20time%2C%20they%20would%20rely%20on%20either%20savings%20or%20borrowing%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20back%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegardless%2C%20that%20would%20not%20be%20a%20sustainable%20solution.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20already%20used%20up%20most%20of%20my%20savings%20and%20have%20started%20borrowing%20small%20amounts%20from%20my%20roommate.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20long%20I%20can%20go%20on%20like%20this%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Rohan%20and%20he%20added%20that%20he%20feels%20guilty%20asking%20his%20parents%20for%20money%2C%20but%20he%20might%20have%20to%20do%20it%20soon%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20also%20highlighted%20mental%20health%20concerns%20as%20students%20feel%20overwhelmed%20by%20their%20financial%20and%20emotional%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20agreed%20to%20take%20in%20undocumented%20Indian%20nationals%20from%20the%20US%2C%20following%20policies%20that%20may%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20deportation%20of%20thousands.%20External%20affairs%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20confirmed%20the%20same%20amid%20ongoing%20immigration%20deliberations%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20caution%20you%20about%20%5Bthe%20numbers%5D%20because%20for%20us%2C%20a%20number%20is%20operative%20when%20we%20can%20actually%20validate%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20individual%20concerned%20is%20of%20Indian%20origin%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737732180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fdsco21d_donald-trump-afp_625x300_24_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famid-donald-trumps-deportation-plans-why-indians-are-quitting-part-time-jobs-7551105%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20students%20said%20that%20they%20will%20assess%20the%20current%20situation%20before%20deciding%20whether%20to%20restart%20their%20part-time%20jobs.%20Till%20that%20time%2C%20they%20would%20rely%20on%20either%20savings%20or%20borrowing%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20back%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-new