quot%3Bunethical%26quot%3B%20and%20could%20harm%20both%20the%20mother%20and%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20significant%20executive%20orders%20that%20Trump%20signed%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20was%20on%20birthright%20citizenship%2C%20bypassing%20the%2014th%20Amendment%20of%20the%20US%20Constitution%20which%20states%20that%20people%20born%20within%20the%20US%20will%20automatically%20be%20American%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20executive%20order%20says%20that%20if%20a%20baby%20is%20born%20to%20a%20mother%20who%20is%20%26quot%3Bunlawfully%20present%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20if%20the%20father%20is%20not%20a%20US%20citizen%20or%20lawful%20permanent%20resident%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20baby's%20birth%2C%20the%20child%20will%20not%20be%20an%20American%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20would%20also%20apply%20to%20those%20babies%20whose%20mothers%20are%20in%20the%20US%20legally%20but%20on%20temporary%20visas%20such%20as%20student%2C%20work%2C%20or%20tourism%20and%20the%20father%20is%20not%20a%20United%20States%20citizen%20or%20a%20Green%20Card%20holder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Gupta%20said%20he%20%E2%80%9Cheard%20such%20things%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20news.%20%E2%80%9CThat's%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20cautioning%20against%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20somebody%20is%20waiting%20for%20elective%20cesarean%20section%20then%20the%20date%20can%20be%20adjusted%20by%20a%20few%20days%2C%20less%20than%20a%20week%20or%20so%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20can%20be%20preponed%20if%20somebody%20is%20seven%20or%20eight%20months%20pregnant.%20They%20cannot%20have%20pre-term%20delivery%20because%20it's%20not%20healthy%20for%20the%20mother%20nor%20the%20child%2C%20and%20the%20child%20may%20end%20up%20in%20the%20neonatal%20intensive%20care%20unit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Gupta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20think%20any%20obstetrician%20will%20agree%20to%20that%20because%20it%20would%20be%20considered%20a%20malpractice.%20And%20they%20are%20liable%20till%20the%20child%20gets%20to%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20so%20nobody%20will%20take%20that%20risk.%E2%80%9D%20He%20said%20that%20if%20there%20is%20an%20injury%20in%20some%20way%20to%20the%20child%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20could%20come%20to%20a%20penalty%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars.%20So%20it's%20simply%20not%20tenable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20such%20a%20medical%20procedure%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cunethical%E2%80%9D%20and%20would%20not%20be%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20the%20child%20or%20the%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20could%20impact%20several%20expectant%20Indian%20couples%20who%20are%20in%20the%20US%20on%20H1-B%20and%20other%20work%20visas%20as%20their%20children%20born%20in%20the%20US%20would%20not%20be%20considered%20American%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20would%20have%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20February%2019%20but%20a%20federal%20judge%20in%20Seattle%20has%20temporarily%20blocked%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20states%20across%20the%20US%2C%20including%20New%20York%2C%20have%20also%20sued%20to%20block%20Trump's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%20announced%20that%20she%20and%20a%20coalition%20of%2018%20states%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20city%20of%20San%20Francisco%2C%20are%20challenging%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20ending%20birthright%20citizenship%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20constitutional%20right%20given%20to%20all%20children%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttorney%20General%20James%20and%20the%20coalition%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20in%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Massachusetts%20seeking%20to%20stop%20the%20president's%20%26quot%3Bunlawful%20action%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20violates%20the%2014th%20Amendment%20of%20the%20US%20Constitution%20and%20%26quot%3Bwill%20harm%20American%20children%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Gupta%20said%20his%20message%20would%20be%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20not%20advisable%20to%20do%20that%20and%20they%20should%20refrain%20from%20doing%20it.%20They%20should%20listen%20to%20their%20obstetrician%20and%20see%20what%20she%20has%20to%20say%20about%20it.%20The%20primary%20concern%20should%20be%20the%20health%20of%20the%20mother%20and%20the%20child%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20may%20not%20even%20stand%20in%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20children%20born%20to%20illegal%20immigrants%20is%20another%20matter%20but%20people%20who%20are%20here%20legally%20on%20H1-B%20visas%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20will%20apply%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737730140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fas4i2ego_newborn-baby-generic_625x300_28_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-american-doctor-warns-against-pre-term-deliveries-over-trumps-birthright-citizenship-order-7550603%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20leading%20doctor%20in%20New%20York%20has%20cautioned%20against%20early%20cesarean%20deliveries%20amid%20concern%20that%20some%20women%20might%20opt%20for%20the%20procedure%20to%20beat%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20ending%20birthright%20citizenship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-american-doctor-warns-against-pre-term-deliveries-over-trumps-birthright-citizenship-order-7550603%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20to%20visit%20wildfires%20affected%20LA%3B%20threatens%20aid%20cut%20over%20%E2%80%9