%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorres-jewellery-case-ed-freezes-bank-deposits-assets-worth-rs-21-cr-125012401330_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FIR%20alleged%20that%20the%20company%20and%20its%20promoters%20%26quot%3Blured%26quot%3B%20investors%20with%20promises%20of%20high%20returns%20ranging%20from%202-9%20per%20cent%20weekly%20on%20investments%20in%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20diamond%20jewellery%2C%20and%20gemstones%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorres-jewellery-case-ed-freezes-bank-deposits-assets-worth-rs-21-cr-125012401330_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Could%20Use%20It%20As%20%26quot%3BWater%20Bomb%26quot%3B%3A%20Arunachal%20Chief%20Minister%20On%20Dam%20Project%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20his%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20counterpart%20Pema%20Khandu%20has%20raised%20concern%20about%20China's%20plan%20to%20construct%20the%20largest%20hydropower%20dam%20in%20eastern%20Tibet%2C%20warning%20that%20it%20could%20be%20used%20by%20Beijing%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwater%20bomb%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20inaugural%20function%20of%20a%20seminar%20titled%20'Environment%20and%20Security'%20in%20the%20state%20Legislative%20Assembly%20complex%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Khandu%20drew%20the%20attention%20of%20all%20stakeholders%20towards%20the%20Chinese%20plan%20to%20construct%20the%20hydropower%20project%20-%20which%20can%20generate%2060%2C000%20MW%20of%20power%20-%20on%20the%20Yarlung%20Tsangpo%20river%2C%20which%20enters%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20as%20the%20Siang%20river%20and%20becomes%20the%20Brahmaputra%20in%20Assam%20before%20flowing%20into%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20later%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3B60%2C000%20MW...%20this%20is%20out%20of%20context.%20If%20such%20a%20big%20mega%20project%20is%20constructed%20there%2C%20it%20will%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20the%20ecology%20of%20areas%20around%20the%20Siang%20and%20the%20Brahmaputra.%20This%20is%20a%20big%20threat%20and%2C%20if%20China%20uses%20this%20as%20a%20water%20bomb%2C%20the%20Adi%20tribe%20that%20we%20have%20in%20the%20Siang%20belt%20will%20disappear%20and%20lakhs%20of%20people%20will%20lose%20their%20lives%20in%20Assam...%20it%20will%20go%20till%20Bangladesh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khandu%20said%20that%2C%20keeping%20China's%20activities%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20Siang%20Upper%20Multipurpose%20Project%20-%20which%20will%20involve%20the%20construction%20of%20dams%20to%20generate%2011%2C000%20MW%20of%20hydroelectric%20power%20project%20-%20as%20a%20national%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20talking%20to%20stakeholders%20about%20this%20so%20that%20we%20can%20maintain%20our%20water%20security%20and%20defend%20against%20China's%20dam%20being%20used%20as%20a%20water%20bomb.%20We%20can't%20trust%20China.%20We%20promote%20peace%20and%20non-violence%20and%20want%20good%20relations%20but%2C%20given%20the%20history%2C%20can%20we%20rely%20on%20China%3F%20That%20is%20a%20big%20question%20mark.%20Look%20at%20their%20expansionist%20theory%2C%20their%20overexploitation%20of%20natural%20resources%20in%20Tibet%20and%20their%20recent%20declaration%20of%20'counties'%20including%20parts%20of%20Ladakh.%20So%20we%20can't%20rely%20on%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20said%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20is%20discussing%20the%20dam%20issue%20with%20China%20through%20diplomatic%20channels%20but%20insisted%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20prepared%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khandu%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20dam%20would%20allow%20China%20to%20control%20the%20timing%20and%20volume%20of%20water%20flowing%20downstream%2C%20which%20could%20have%20devastating%20effects%20during%20periods%20of%20low%20flow%20or%20drought.%20The%20mighty%20Siang%20and%20Brahmaputra%20rivers%20could%20dry%20up%20during%20winters%2C%20disrupting%20life%20in%20the%20Siang%20belt%20and%20the%20plains%20of%20Assam%2C%20he%20cautioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20Mr%20Khandu%20said%2C%20sudden%20releases%20of%20water%20from%20the%20dam%20could%20cause%20severe%20flooding%20downstream%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20monsoon%2C%20displacing%20communities%2C%20destroying%20crops%20and%20damaging%20infrastructure.%20The%20dam%2C%20he%20emphasised%2C%20would%20alter%20the%20sediment%20flow%2C%20affecting%20agricultural%20lands%20that%20rely%20on%20the%20river's%20natural%20replenishment%20of%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Communicated%20Concern'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20dam%2C%20whose%20construction%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20Chinese%20government%20in%20December%2C%20will%20span%20a%20gorge%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20in%20eastern%20Tibet%2C%20where%20the%20Brahmaputra%20River%20makes%20a%20U-turn%20to%20flow%20into%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20dam's%20possible%20impact%20on%20Assam%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20we%20are%20concerned%2C%20we%20have%20already%20communicated%20that%20if%20this%20dam%20comes%20up%2C%20the%20Brahmaputra%20ecosystem%20will%20become%20completely%20fragile%2C%20it%20will%20become%20dry%20and%20we%20will%20only%20depend%20on%20the%20rainwater%20of%20Bhutan%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20already%20communicated%20its%20concern%20to%20the%20Chinese%20side.%20And%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20in%20the%20dialogue%20process%20which%20is%20presently%20going%20on%20between%20India%20and%20China%2C%20this%20will%20be%20definitely%20raised%20by%20the%20Indian%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737729660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ftfgg10k_three-gorges-dam-of-china_625x300_27_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flargest-hydropower-dam-china-dam-yarlung-tsangpo-tibet-pema-khandu-china-could-use-it-as-water-bomb-arunachal-chief-minister-on-dam-project-7550761%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20his%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20counterpart%20Pema%20Khandu%20has%20raised%20concern%20about%20China's%20plan%20to%20construct%20the%20largest%20hydropower%20dam%20in%20eastern%20Tibet%2C%20warning%20that%20it%20could%20be%20used%20by%20Beijing%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwater%20bomb%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flargest-hydropower-dam-china-dam-yarlung-tsangpo-tibet-pema-khandu-china-could-use-it-as-water-bomb-arunachal-chief-minister-on-dam-project-7550761%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Junaid%20sat%20outside%20during%20Ira's%20wedding%20with%20Nupur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737729610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117527538%2Cimgsize-54006.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjunaid-khan-reveals-he-sat-outside-during-sister-ira-khans-wedding-with-nupur-shikhare-aamir-khan-suggested-him-to-elope-if-he-plans-to-marry%2Farticleshow%2F117527538.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117527538.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJunaid%20Khan%2C%20son%20of%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20is%20promoting%20his%20debut%20film%