ning%20without%20issue%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20doctor%20had%20simply%20%26quot%3Bpanicked%20and%20recorded%20a%20video%26quot%3B.%20The%20hospital%20staff%20must%20stay%20%26quot%3Bfocussed%20on%20patient%20care%20at%20all%20times%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20power%20backup%20systems%20at%20Rajindra%20hospital%2C%20Patiala%20are%20multi%20level%20(3%20hotlines)%20%26amp%3B%20functioning%20without%20issue.%20Today%2C%20a%20local%20fault%20led%20to%20momentary%20loss%20of%20electricity.%20The%20UPS%20and%20generator%20backup%20functioned%20seamlessly%20%26amp%3B%20the%20surgery%20was%20conducted%20without%20issue.%20Patient%20is%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgPmjJy9R5x%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FgPmjJy9R5x%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Balbir%20Singh%20(%40AAPbalbir)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAAPbalbir%2Fstatus%2F1882758581734232215%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2024%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2056-second%20clip%2C%20the%20doctor%20in%20the%20OT%20is%20heard%20saying%20that%20such%20cases%20of%20power%20outages%20tend%20to%20recur%20at%20the%20hospital.%20It%20could%20not%20be%20immediately%20ascertained%20when%20the%20video%20was%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20such%20a%20thing%20is%20happening%20(power%20outage).%20It's%20been%2015%20minutes%20since%20the%20power%20went%20out.%20The%20ventilator%20has%20also%20shut%20down.%20If%20anything%20happens%20to%20the%20patient%2C%20who%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20this%3F%20The%20doctors%3F%20All%20the%20staff%20are%20standing%20here%2C%20the%20ventilator%20has%20turned%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20power%20supply%20is%20often%20disrupted%20in%20the%2