20company%20are%20sports%20cars%2C%20which%20are%20produced%20in-house%20in%20designated%20production%20facilities.%20In%20July%202017%2C%20McLaren%20Automotive%20became%20a%20wholly-owned%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20wider%20McLaren%20Group%2C%20which%20is%20wholly%20owned%20by%20Mumtalakat%20Holding%20Company%2C%20the%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Bahrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20price%20of%20McLaren%20cars%20start%20from%20Rs%204.5%20crore%20for%20the%20GT%2C%20while%20the%20most%20expensive%20McLaren%20(the%20newest%20model%20750S)%20is%20priced%20Rs%205.91%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737727200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fpag5qkbo_mclaren-drive_625x300_24_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwow-mclarens-special-drive-to-celebrate-50-supercar-mark-thrills-internet-7550459%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20those%20watching%2C%20it%20wasn't%20just%20a%20race%20-%20it%20was%20a%20spectacle%2C%20a%20moment%20where%20luxury%20and%20adrenaline%20merged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwow-mclarens-special-drive-to-celebrate-50-supercar-mark-thrills-internet-7550459%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEnsure%20Fair%20Proceedings%26quot%3B%3A%20Suspended%20MPs%20To%20Speaker%20After%20Waqf%20Panel%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOpposition%20members%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20panel%20on%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20who%20were%20suspended%20for%20a%20day%20today%20amid%20continuous%20protests%20and%20accusations%20against%20Chairman%20Jagdambika%20Pal%20of%20steam-rolling%20through%20the%20proceedings%2C%20have%20written%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20seeking%20proceedings%20to%20be%20conducted%20in%20a%20fair%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20all%20felt%20humiliated%2C%20we%20stood%20and%20raised%20our%20voice%20democratically%20to%20hear%20our%20demands.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Chairman%20spoke%20in%20phone%20with%20somebody%20and%20suddenly%20and%20surprisingly%2C%20he%20ordered%20our%20suspension%20with%20shouting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20suspended%20MPs%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20The%20Amendments%20proposed%20in%20the%20Bill%20are%20not%20only%20connected%20with%20the%20huge%20land%20banks%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Boards%20across%20the%20country%2C%20but%20also%20relevant%20to%20the%20judicial%20pronouncements%20of%20the%20High%20Courts%2FSupreme%20Court%20thereon%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStatues%20and%20rules%20enacted%20by%20various%20state%20governments%20in%20this%20regard%20are%20also%20in%20challenge%20whereby%20conflict%20of%20interest%20has%20arisen%20thereto.%20Hence%2C%20a%20comprehensive%20study%20is%20essentially%20needed%20by%20the%20JPC%20to%20address%20these%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20stakeholders%20in%20a%20holistic%20manner.%20In%20these%20circumstances%2C%20rushing%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20JPC%20without%20application%20of%20the%20mind%20by%20the%20Chairman%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20riddle%20wrapped%20with%20hidden%20malice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MPs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspended%20members%20of%20the%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%20(JPC)%20are%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%2C%20Mohammad%20Jawed%2C%20A%20Raja%2C%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20Naseer%20Hussain%2C%20Mohibullah%2C%20Mohamed%20Abdullah%2C%20Arvind%20Sawant%2C%20Nadeem-ul%20Haque%2C%20and%20Imran%20Masood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20the%20Opposition%20members%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20a%20delegation%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20led%20by%20Mirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%2C%20the%20religious%20head%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20appeared%20before%20the%20joint%20committee%20on%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20to%20share%20their%20concerns%20about%20the%20draft%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20BJP%20member%20Aparajita%20Sarangi%20said%20the%20conduct%20of%20Opposition%20members%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisgusting%26quot%3B%20as%20they%20were%20continuously%20creating%20ruckus%20during%20the%20meeting%20and%20using%20unparliamentary%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20JPC%20on%20August%208%2C%202024%20following%20its%20introduction%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju.%20The%20bill%20aims%20to%20amend%20the%20Waqf%20Act%2C%201995%2C%20to%20address%20issues%20and%20challenges%20in%20regulating%20and%20managing%20Waqf%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20appearing%20before%20the%20committee%2C%20Mirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20bill%20and%20favoured%20non-interference%20by%20the%20government%20in%20matters%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20our%20suggestions%20would%20be%20heard%20and%20acted%20upon%20and%20no%20such%20step%20would%20be%20taken%20that%20would%20make%20Muslims%20feel%20that%20they%20are%20being%20disempowered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737726720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fbv2pgbe8_waqf-meet_625x300_14_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconduct-proceedings-in-fair-transparent-manner-suspended-opposition-mps-write-to-speaker-after-waqf-panel-meet-7550302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20meeting%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20began%20on%20a%20rough%20note%20today%2C%20with%20Opposition%20members%20claiming%20they%20were%20not%20being%20given%20adequate%20time%20to%20study%20the%20proposed%20changes%20to%20the%20draft%20legislation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findi